{"tid":2250488,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"籲港堅持 抗警暴屬「漫長鬥爭」","createTime":"2020-10-20T06:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T06:43:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"97b3107f02774c4b40d0cea032bfd18aeb38682c","tid":2250488,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201020/UKQ55RLGEJBXTGJAFFTYJ3JTCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201020%2FUKQ55RLGEJBXTGJAFFTYJ3JTCM%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEaFdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=3549eeba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201020%2FUKQ55RLGEJBXTGJAFFTYJ3JTCM%2F&h=017c28ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201020/UKQ55RLGEJBXTGJAFFTYJ3JTCM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n籲港堅持 抗警暴屬「漫長鬥爭」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mZhec8qN2aeTCnJ9vmN3FAu5HoY=/3323x2215/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SUDNWFL5GZDGBLEUEKJUIENW2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmZhec8qN2aeTCnJ9vmN3FAu5HoY%3D%2F3323x2215%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSUDNWFL5GZDGBLEUEKJUIENW2I.jpg&h=1037be08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有團體在弗洛伊德被殺現場附近公園放置了過百個白色膠碑，每個均寫上多年來被警察殺死的受害者名字，大部份為非裔人士。何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n走過位於明尼亞波利斯巿的弗洛伊德被殺現場，紀念廣場上是祭壇、鮮花、紀念字句，甚至有自製的大型雕塑，是感覺熟悉的悼念現場；走遠一點到達團體自發而建的警暴受害者「墳場」，一個個刻上名字「白碑」，遠眺草皮上那彷彿在發聲的「say their names」字句，不禁想起不少令人心痛的名字。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：曾推犯罪法案 被視種族歧視前科  明州黑人票非拜登囊中物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指四警被控屬萬中無一<br />\n<br />\n跟當地人談起香港示威，不少人都知道個大概。當地對抗警暴多年的團體指，明州的種族問題始於60年代，當時已有不少對抗警暴的暴亂發生，都會被警方冷處理，不少警察胡亂殺人後經常沒有後果，如今竟有四名警員被落案控告，實屬萬中無一。<br />\n<br />\n不過，警方一天未落實改革，類似事件仍然有機會重演。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者 鍾雅宜"}]}